Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Tandubas Emergency Hospital in the Municipality of Sapa-Sapa, Province of Tawi-Tawi to Tuan Ligad - Dung Lipae Emergency Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 49
An Act Changing the Name of the Tandubas Emergency Hospital in the Municipality of Sapa-Sapa, Province of Tawi-Tawi to Tuan Ligad - Dung Lipae Emergency Hospital
Section 1. The name of the Tandubas Emergency Hospital in the Municipality of Sapa-Sapa, Province of Tawi-Tawi, is hereby changed to Tuan Ligad- duang Lipae Emergency Hospital.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1Ã¢wphi1
Approved: December 20, 1979
